sets.tps: 64 HP, 12 En, 200 M Atk, 24 R Def, 200 Sp
sets.detail:
200 Melee Attack and Brawny are to hit as hard as possible 
 200 Speed is to be as fast as possible, letting it outspeed slower walls like Stratusoar and Obsidrugon 
 12 Energy = 260 Energy at level 50 for (2 Timber Thrashes + 2 Primal Slashes + 1 Earthquake) 
 64 HP is to be as bulky as possible with what's left while taking minimum Burn damage 
 24 Ranged Defense is leftovers and improves bulk a little
sets.author: Epicly Epic Gamer
